     H            Y.
     F** AL#R10  *******************************************
     F*便でパレットが１種類をパレットＰＵＬＬＩＮＧに    *
     F*      ITS.        2015.06.03                        *
     F******************************************************
     FAL#WP11 UF  E           K        DISK
     FAL#WP10 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        1   60STIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------
      *  MAIN ROUTINE
      *-----------------------------------------------------
     C                     TIME           WTIME
      *
     C                     READ AL#WP111                 81
     C           *IN81     DOWEQ'0'
     C                     EXSR #SB400
     C                     READ AL#WP111                 81
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------
      * AL#WP10
      *-----------------------------------------------------
     CSR         #SB400    BEGSR
      *
     C           KEYCA     KLIST
JW   C                     KFLD           W1SHID
     C                     KFLD           W1TRKB
     C                     KFLD           W1SURT
     C           KEYCA     CHAINAL#WP101             90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ '0'
     C           W0KPLT    IFEQ 1
     C                     MOVEL'1'       W1PPUL
     C                     UPDATAL#WP111
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      *
     CSR         ESB400    ENDSR
